"{\"uid\": \"leaderlive.co.uk-news-24328349.jade-jones-opens-golden-gates-flint-high-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Jade JonesCelebritiesEducationFlintshire  FLINT'S very own Jade Jones opened the new golden gates at her old school ahead of her bid to win gold at Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The prospect of\\u00a0becoming the first taekwondo athlete in history to win three Olympic gold medals awaits\\u00a0Flint's Jade Jones in Paris next year.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 265, \"end\": 270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"score\": 0.9999999996359747, \"rank\": 3.638428704926895e-10, \"text\": \"Flint\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\"}, {\"begin\": 273, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Jones-Hall\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.935006482400996e-14, \"text\": \"Jade Jones\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Jones-Hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Jones-Hall\"}, {\"begin\": 287, \"end\": 292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999971708633896, \"rank\": 2.8291445646957906e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jones won her first Olympic title as a teenager at London 2012 and followed that up with another four years later.\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 356, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999990007807346, \"rank\": 9.984818004433308e-07, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old was awarded an OBE at the start of 2023\\u00a0and is considered a hero by many, including by those in her hometown of Flint.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 452, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 2.4457203241294035e-11, \"text\": \"OBE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\"}, {\"begin\": 549, \"end\": 554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"score\": 0.9999999996359747, \"rank\": 3.638428704926895e-10, \"text\": \"Flint\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now living in Croatia to prepare for this year's Olympic games, Jade took a break from training to visit her old school, Flint High.\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 571, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia\", \"score\": 0.99529907734866, \"rank\": 0.004694220863779148, \"text\": \"Croatia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia\"}, {\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade\", \"score\": 0.6498435863311186, \"rank\": 0.4889735646174867, \"text\": \"Jade\", \"types\": [\"Q7946\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade\"}, {\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"score\": 0.9999999996359747, \"rank\": 3.638428704926895e-10, \"text\": \"Flint\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today (Friday, May 17)\\u00a0 Jade opened the new golden gates at the school, that have been organised in honour of the hometown star.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jade was joined by Mayor of Flint, Ben Goldsborough, Deputy Mayor, Mel Buckley, Carolyn Thomas MS as well as pupils and staff from the school.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 851, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"score\": 0.9999999996359747, \"rank\": 3.638428704926895e-10, \"text\": \"Flint\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\"}, {\"begin\": 862, \"end\": 874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goldsborough_Hall\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.4470896144259563e-13, \"text\": \"Goldsborough\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goldsborough_Hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goldsborough_Hall\"}, {\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_F._Buckley_Jr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999998603926, \"rank\": 7.394053653951221e-11, \"text\": \"Buckley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_F._Buckley_Jr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_F._Buckley_Jr.\"}, {\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolyn_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9999990239532723, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carolyn Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolyn_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolyn_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"score\": 0.9977457611168776, \"rank\": 0.0013009059547434319, \"text\": \"MS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pupils quizzed her on her career to date and plans for Paris later this year.\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1022, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999971708633896, \"rank\": 2.8291445646957906e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jade Jones with staff at Flint High(Image: NQ)  Speaking at the ceremony, Jade Jones said: \\\"It feels lovely to be back and\\u00a0especially with the golden gates.\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1071, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"score\": 0.9999999996359747, \"rank\": 3.638428704926895e-10, \"text\": \"Flint\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\"}, {\"begin\": 1120, \"end\": 1130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Jones-Hall\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.935006482400996e-14, \"text\": \"Jade Jones\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Jones-Hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Jones-Hall\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Flint has always supported me, it's my hometown and I am really proud to be from here so to be back before the Olympics inspires me.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1205, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"score\": 0.9999999996359747, \"rank\": 3.638428704926895e-10, \"text\": \"Flint\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It really gives me a strength knowing where I am from, everybody willing me on, how can I not go for it and give it my everything.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MOST READ:  \\\"It's about remembering London and Rio, obviously Tokyo did not go to plan but just getting that belief and thinking 'imagine coming back with the medal', it would be amazing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.999999535800151, \"rank\": 2.2570011262295745e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1519, \"end\": 1522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9977470745583321, \"rank\": 0.002258011670249884, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8931343967191571, \"rank\": 0.11939981886589046, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mayor of Flint, Cllr Ben Goldsborough added: \\\"Thank you Jade for coming, you really are an inspiration to the town and what you have been able to give to us.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1671, \"end\": 1676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"score\": 0.9999999996359747, \"rank\": 3.638428704926895e-10, \"text\": \"Flint\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\"}, {\"begin\": 1687, \"end\": 1699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goldsborough_Hall\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.4470896144259563e-13, \"text\": \"Goldsborough\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goldsborough_Hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goldsborough_Hall\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have shown that through putting dedication and hard graft in you can achieve what you want to achieve what you want to and I know that when it comes to a couple of months time when you are out in Paris we are going to be all routing for you again because we always are.\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 2095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2022, \"end\": 2027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999971708633896, \"rank\": 2.8291445646957906e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The only problem is we are going to run out of buildings to name after you when you win again, so best of luck.\\\"\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This website and associated newspapers adhere to the Independent Press Standards Organisation's     Editors' Code of Practice.\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have a complaint about the editorial content which relates to     inaccuracy or intrusion, then pleasecontact the editor here.\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are dissatisfied with the response provided you cancontact IPSO here  \\u00a9 2001-2025.\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Leaderis owned and operated by Newsquest Media Group Ltd, an audited local newspaper network.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2604, \"end\": 2629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Newsquest Media Group Ltd\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbped